 Cell[BoxData[
 "BreakInMonomials"],ExpressionUUID->"be4f3fe2-0327-4bae-8f9b-fd7d79a696b5"],
 " can decompose an expression into monomials, which is useful to analyse the \
structure of contractions."
}], "Text",
